Class TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.Substitutor.ForDetachment

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor<TypeDescription.Generic>
    Enclosing class:
    TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.Substitutor

    public static class TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.Substitutor.ForDetachment
extends TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.Substitutor
    A visitor for detaching a type from its declaration context by detaching type variables. This is achieved by detaching type variables and by replacing the declaring type which is identified by a provided ElementMatcher with TargetType.
